		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="25.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Step 3. Hold the indicators workshop">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this step, the core team will hold the indicators workshop with community member participants.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;We will learn from the participants where systems and topics fall on resilience and equity continuums.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;Detailed instructions are ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="here"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch4_Instructions.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="&#xD;1. At the workshop, divide into groups for each system (or topic). Have the breakout groups sort the indicator cards and place them into resilience and equity diagrams.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="&#xD;2. Think back to Chapter 3 stories">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- In what aspects/areas did you hear about least/greatest resiliency?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- In what aspects/areas did you hear about least/greatest equity?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- How might these stories change/inform your indicator sorting?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
	</container>
